subtitleNullable: Perform Text Classification in Gujarati using this Dataset
descriptionNullable:
This data set contains ~6500 news article headlines which I had collected from Gujarati news websites.

The data set has been cleaned and contains train and test set using which you can benchmark your classification models in Gujarati

The scripts which were used to create the data set can be found [here](https://github.com/goru001/nlp-for-gujarati/tree/master/datasets-preparation)
